## Multimodal

`src/{{ package_name }}/data/image_text.py` builds (image, token_ids) loaders from any HF hub dataset with CLIP-matched preprocessing, and pairs with the CLIP-style objective:

```bash
uv run python src/{{ package_name }}/train.py loss=contrastive
```

Data-loading escalation path: HF `datasets` → LitData / MosaicML streaming (cloud shards, mid-epoch resume) → WebDataset (archival interop). Start at step 1; move only when it hurts.

